Another thing, as the opposing faction it is your job to prove that root for mages it is overpowered not mine. I'm not going to do your job for you. <br>
<br>
Your examples that try to show that root would make mages overpowered only shows that a good player of any class that has root can do getto crowd control. Necros, shamans and druids have mana free dots from epic; they can root a bunch of mobs and cook them all with it and be full mana when they are done. I think that is more overpowered. <br>
<br>
Will root let mages do some places they couldn't do before? Yes, so what? Other classes can do it now and better. Will root change the way a mage solo? No, but it will make it safer. <br>
<br>
